  <section class="about">
    <h2>About the Photographer</h2>
    <p>Hi, I'm Shanmukha Sai, a passionate photographer who loves capturing calm and fleeting moments. My photography focuses on natural light, minimal compositions, and quiet beauty found in everyday life. Whether it’s a morning harbor, an empty street, or a portrait by the window, I try to preserve emotions that words can’t express.</p>
    <p>This collection showcases my favorite works over the past few years — from serene landscapes to intimate portraits. I hope you enjoy browsing through them as much as I enjoyed creating them.</p>
  </section>

